from PyPDF2 import PdfReader
pdf_path = './8-StepLength/stepLength-main/paper.pdf'
reader = PdfReader(pdf_path)
num_pages = len(reader.pages)
text = ''
for i in range(min(num_pages, 5)):
    text += reader.pages[i].extract_text() + '\n'
print(text[:2000])
